{
  "metadata": {
    "stage": "2_two_phase_pinn",
    "version": "v4.6-standard",
    "created_at": "2026-05-20",
    "description": "合并 v4.5-standard (Fourier+阶段划分+高数据权重) 与 v4.5-physics-sampling (physics_based采样+高物理权重) 的优点，配合 relu² 空间约束修复",
    "key_changes_from_v4.5": [
      "use_fourier: true (v4.5-physics-sampling错误设为false, 导致无法表达径向开口)",
      "physics_based 采样 (电压分区+自适应时间常数, 替代均匀采样)",
      "物理权重提升: ns 0.1→0.5, continuity 0.5→2.0, vof 0.5→3.0",
      "新增 S3 表面约束 top-level 权重 (electrowetting/laplace/sidewall等)",
      "resample_interval: 5000 (防止对固定采样点过拟合)",
      "代码修复(不在config): sigmoid→relu², EWD力方向正确, AC mobility 1e-8→1e-7"
    ]
  },
  "model": {
    "input_format": "triplet",
